[23.476468, "o", "\u001b[1;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[3;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[4;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[5;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[6;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\u001b[0m\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1m\u001b[96mBrainyard TUI\u001b[0m\u001b[2m — \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[36mresearch-agent\u001b[0m\u001b[2m · \u001b[0m\u001b[95mclaude-code/opus\u001b[0m\u001b[2m · \u001b[0m\u001b[2msession tutorial-15-research\u001b[0m \u001b[2m│\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2mType /help for commands. AI output may be inaccurate.\u001b[0m                            \u001b[2m│\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[1m\u001b[96m\u001b[100m❯ Research whether add"]
[23.476478, "o", "ing a --json output option to this CLI is feasible. Use ONLY your explore specialist to\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K  map how greetings are currently rendered across the files, thread the finding into your research dossier,\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K  then finalize with a short feasibility recommendation. Do NOT run the plan, todo, exec, or update\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K  specialists and do NOT write any code into the project — investigate and recommend only.\u001b[0m\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(37305 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(15.7s)\u001b[0m\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mIteration 1 — no history. The task is tightly scoped: investigate feasibility of adding a `--json` \u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2moutput option to a CLI, but the actual investigative work is to map how greetings are rendered \u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2macross files using ONLY explore-agent, thread findings into the dossier, then finalize with a \u001b[0m\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mfeasibility recommendation. Constraints: no plan/todo/exec/update specialists, no code w"]
[23.476509, "o", "ritten into \u001b[0m\u001b[26;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mthe project. My only fixed obligation on iter 1 is dossier bootstrap. Let me compute the \u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mdeterministic id, probe for an existing dossier, and bootstrap if absent. I'll define acceptance \u001b[0m\u001b[28;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mcriteria reflecting the constrained scope: (a1) map how greetings are currently rendered across \u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mfiles via explore-agent, (a2) thread the finding into the dossier, (a3) deliver a short feasibility \u001b[0m\u001b[30;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mrecommendation for --json. Direction bullets reflect the explore-only constraint.\u001b[0m\u001b[31;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;93m⠏\u001b[0m\u001b[2m]\u001b[0m \u001b[96mDeliberating...\u001b[0m\u001b[2m (15.6s)\u001b[0m"]
[23.476589, "o", "\u001b[32;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m"]
[23.482102, "o", "\u001b[1;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(def rid (:slug (research$id :question \"Research whether adding a --json output option to this CLI is\u001b[0m\u001b[2;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mfeasible. Map how greetings are currently rendered across the files.\")))\u001b[0m\u001b[3;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m\u001b[0m\u001b[4;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(def state (research$resume? :id rid))\u001b[0m\u001b[5;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m\u001b[0m\u001b[6;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(println \"rid:\" rid)\u001b[0m\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(println \"resume-state:\" (pr-str state))\u001b[0m\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m\u001b[0m\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(if (:exists? state)\u001b[0m\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  :resume\u001b[0m\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  (research$bootstrap\u001b[0m\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m    :id rid\u001b[0m\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m    :purpose \"Research whether adding a --json output option to this CLI is feasible. Use ONLY the\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mexplore specialist to map how greetings are currently rendered across the files, thread the finding\u001b[0m"]
[23.482114, "o", "\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35minto the research dossier, then finalize with a short feasibility recommendation. Do NOT run\u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mplan/todo/exec/update specialists and do NOT write any code into the project — investigate and\u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mrecommend only.\"\u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m    :acceptance [{:id \"a1\" :text \"Map how greetings are currently rendered across the CLI files (which\u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mfiles, which functions, what output mechanism) using ONLY explore-agent.\" :status :open}\u001b[0m\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m                 {:id \"a2\" :text \"Thread the explore finding into the research dossier (findings.log +\u001b[0m\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mdossier body).\" :status :open}\u001b[0m\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m                 {:id \"a3\" :text \"Deliver a short, evidence-cited feasibility recommendation for adding\u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35ma --json output option.\" :status :open}]\u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35"]
