[141.867313, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1m\u001b[96mBrainyard TUI\u001b[0m\u001b[2m — \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[36mresearch-agent\u001b[0m\u001b[2m · \u001b[0m\u001b[95mclaude-code/opus\u001b[0m\u001b[2m · \u001b[0m\u001b[2msession tutorial-15-research\u001b[0m \u001b[2m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2mType /help for commands. AI output may be inaccurate.\u001b[0m                            \u001b[2m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[96m\u001b[100m❯ Research whether adding a --json output option to this CLI is feasible. Use ONLY your explore specialist to\r\n  map how greetings are currently rendered across the files, thread the findi"]
[141.867328, "o", "ng into your research dossier,\r\n  then finalize with a short feasibility recommendation. Do NOT run the plan, todo, exec, or update\r\n  specialists and do NOT write any code into the project — investigate and recommend only.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(37305 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(15.7s)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mIteration 1 — no history. The task is tightly scoped: investigate feasibility of adding a `--json` \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2moutput option to a CLI, but the actual investigative work is to map how greetings are rendered \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2macross files using ONLY explore-agent, thread findings into the dossier, then finalize with a \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mfeasibility recommendation. Constraints: no plan/todo/exec/update specialists, no code written into \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mthe project. My only fixed obligation on iter 1 is dossier bootstrap. Let me compute the \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mdeterministic id, probe for an existing dossier, and bootstrap if absent. I'll define acceptance \u001b["]
[141.867354, "o", "0m\r\n         \u001b[2mcriteria reflecting the constrained scope: (a1) map how greetings are currently rendered across \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mfiles via explore-agent, (a2) thread the finding into the dossier, (a3) deliver a short feasibility \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mrecommendation for --json. Direction bullets reflect the explore-only constraint.\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m• Code:\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m┌─\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(def rid (:slug (research$id :question \"Research whether adding a --json output option to this CLI is\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35mfeasible. Map how greetings are currently rendered across the files.\")))\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(def state (research$resume? :id rid))\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(println \"rid:\" rid)\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(println \"resume-state:\" (pr-str state))\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m(if (:exists? state)\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  :resume\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m  (research$bootstrap\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[2m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[35m    :i"]
